com.clarkparsia.openrdf
Class ContextAwareStatement

java.lang.Object
  com.clarkparsia.openrdf.ContextAwareStatement
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, Statement
public final class ContextAwareStatement
extends java.lang.Object
implements Statement

Implementation of a Sesame Statement which takes into account the context for equals(java.lang.Object) but not hashCode() so it is still compatible with default Sesame implementations.

0.4.1
